data.description: This is a beautiful must see in the heart of Sneads. This historic, 3 bedroom 1 bath home has all the charm. Original, 1930 real hardwood floors throughout, large bedrooms with oversized closet/storage space. Large open kitchen with upgraded tile. All new windows in 2015,NEW Roof, HVAC and Gas fireplace all in 2019. Also equipped with outdoor fun to relax in an above ground pool and beautiful yard and small pavilion for shade. In addition to the home, this property also has a 1,200 sqft mixed use building on the West side of the lot. Previously serving multiple business ventures, the floor plan offers an adaptable layout that can be used as a commercial rental or personal storage. It is a concrete block build with a ribbed tin roof, plumbed for utilities, equipped w/central heat and A/C.
